name: Thor
message: You have no idea who you're dealing with

name: Tony
message: Shakespear in the park? Doth mother know, you weareth her drapes?

name: Bruce
noteText: In case you needed to kill me, but you can't! I know! I tried!... I got low. I didn't see an end, so I put a bullet in my mouth... and the other guy spit it out! So I moved on. I focused on helping other people. I was good, until you dragged me back into this freak show and put everyone here at risk!

name: Natasha
message: Hey there big guy! The sun's getting real low
